{"name":"Cowboy","size":"medium","type":"humanoid","tag":"Badlands","alignment":"any alignment","hitDice":"5","armorName":"leather armor","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":9,"otherArmorDesc":"10","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"22 (5d8)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"16","dexPoints":"16","conPoints":"14","intPoints":"8","wisPoints":"12","chaPoints":"12","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"3","customCr":"1 (200 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The monster can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The monster regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the monster can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the monster can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The monster can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the monster's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the monster's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the monster dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Headshot","desc":"[MON] rolls 4x the normal amount of damage die when they Crit."}],"actions":[{"name":"Cattleman Revolver","desc":"The [MON] fires at a creature in the Wild West. [DEX ATK + 1] to hit, range 40/120 ft. _Hit:_ [DEX 2D8] piercing damage."},{"name":"Lasso","desc":"The [MON] lassos a creature within 30ft. They make an athletics check vs the target's athletics or acrobatics check. The creature is **restrained** if they fail the check."}],"bonusActions":[],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"str","order":0},{"name":"dex","order":1}],"skills":[{"name":"athletics","stat":"str","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"intimidation","stat":"cha"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":0,"damage":[]}